   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Mesore 19. Paid for the account of the villagers of Karanis through Syros, son of Komon, for the second new indiction, one-hundred and twenty litrai of chaff, 120, only. I, Diatimos, signed, through me, Philippos, his son.</ab>
